data.description: This home is for sale owner financing! With only $40k down payment and a 8% interest rate, your estimated payment would be $2,975.01 a month for this beautiful two story, three bedroom two bathroom home! The interior features a chef-ready kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinetry. Upstairs, you'll find a spacious master bedroom and bathroom with a tub, shower, and walk-in closet. There are also two other large bedrooms in this cozy, open-concept home. And the best part? It's less than three years old- so foundation warranty is still effective!
